T1: Tumor size is 2.0 cm or less and has not invaded the chest wall or skin
T1a: Tumor size is 0.5 cm or less
T1b: Tumor size is more than 0.5 cm but not more than 1.0 cm
T1c: Tumor size is more than 1.0 cm but not more than 2.0 cm
T2: Tumor size is more than 2.0 cm but not more than 5.0 cm
T3: Tumor size is more than 5.0 cm
T4: Tumor of any size extends to the chest wall and/or skin
